definition: Austria/Austrian/abbr. for 奧地利|奥地利[Ao4 di4 li4]/Olympic/Olympics/abbr. for 奧林匹克|奥林匹克[Ao4 lin2 pi3 ke4]
umber-black dye for painting the eyebrow

sentences.english: When Audrey asked, "Why haven't you approached your manager?"
sentences.chinese: 當奧黛麗問，“你爲什麼不去找你的經理？”

sentences.english: The Audrey II doesn't directly generate any money for Mushnik's Flower Shop.
sentences.chinese: 奧黛麗二世並沒有直接爲穆希尼的花店帶來收益。

sentences.english: One of Audreys most 20)radiant roles was in My Fair Lady (1964).
sentences.chinese: 奧黛麗最亮麗的角色之一是扮演窈窕淑女的女主角。

sentences.english: David's English was very poor while Odelette was very good in both English and German.
sentences.chinese: 戴維德的英語很差，而奧黛麗特精通英語和德語。

sentences.english: Rotbart casts the spell over the Prince and he, deceived by this similarity, declares Odilia his bride.
sentences.chinese: 王子被她相似的外表所欺騙，宣佈奧黛麗爲他的新娘。

sentences.english: And yet without the Audrey II, Mushnik's wouldn't make any sales.
sentences.chinese: 然而，要是沒有奧黛麗二世，穆希尼就賣不出花。
